Generation method (suggested PowerShell snippet — EA-1 may use any equivalent):
```powershell
function Get-DirLocSummary($dir) {
    $files = Get-ChildItem $dir -Recurse -File | Where-Object { $_.Extension -in @('.py','.ps1','.xml','.md','.yaml','.json') }
    @{ file_count = $files.Count; total_loc = ($files | Get-Content | Measure-Object -Line).Lines }
}
```

Place int values inline; do not leave `` literals in committed file. Generated_utc may be derived from `(Get-Date).ToUniversalTime().ToString("yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ")`.
